  "detailed_description": "In <strong>Become a Star</strong>, play a musician on stage in this <strong>rhythm game</strong>! Choose your instrument (<strong>guitar or drums</strong>), plan your gigs, and rock the crowd to the rhythm of original music! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295790/extras/5eecd2a4084921bc5d642898589b968c.avif?t=1712916274\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>A <strong>fun arcade mode</strong>, where you can <strong>select the songs and concert halls</strong>, and simply enjoy the music and the gameplay. <strong>Customize your concerts: pick indoor or outdoor scenes, launch visual effects of your choice</strong>, and perform in a small bar or the famous Bunker Palace.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features</h2><br>- Play Drums Or Guitar <br><br>- 8 concert venues (indoor/outdoor)<br><br>- See the audience react to your performance<br><br>- 21 musics (4 originals)<br><br>- 2 avatars (Kala ans Viktor)",
  "about_the_game": "In <strong>Become a Star</strong>, play a musician on stage in this <strong>rhythm game</strong>! Choose your instrument (<strong>guitar or drums</strong>), plan your gigs, and rock the crowd to the rhythm of original music! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295790/extras/5eecd2a4084921bc5d642898589b968c.avif?t=1712916274\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>A <strong>fun arcade mode</strong>, where you can <strong>select the songs and concert halls</strong>, and simply enjoy the music and the gameplay. <strong>Customize your concerts: pick indoor or outdoor scenes, launch visual effects of your choice</strong>, and perform in a small bar or the famous Bunker Palace.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features</h2><br>- Play Drums Or Guitar <br><br>- 8 concert venues (indoor/outdoor)<br><br>- See the audience react to your performance<br><br>- 21 musics (4 originals)<br><br>- 2 avatars (Kala ans Viktor)",
